docs.title: Daily Quotes and Jokes
docs.text:
🤖 Made with DevOps

This page will be automatically built and deployed to GitHub Page everyday without any human intervention. Therefore, the following quotes and jokes are daily renewed.

Quote Refresh the page... Generate New Prompt Laugh of the Day Why did the programmer quit his job?Because he didn't get arrays.

docs.title: Usage
docs.text:
CSS files with underscore _ are the compiled result from the extra_sass directory, which contains Bootstrap style. - For example, from the root of the repository:

sass docs/extra_sass/_buttons.scss docs/style/_buttons.css
  • Add the compiled file to mkdocs.yml/extra_css
